codex
I have a concrete path now: V2 flashswap `WETH`, unwrap to `ETH`, invoke the target’s payable mint path with nominal `depositAmount == borrowedWETH`, burn the over-minted iTokens for `YFI`, then sell only the minimum `YFI` back to `WETH` on a second V2 pool to repay the flashswap. I’m replacing the verifier with that implementation and keeping explicit state about the loan-token shortfall to show the core causality.
